id: pm-q71q
title: Pin release dependency ranges for Dependabot hygiene
description: Replace direct latest dependency specs with deterministic semver ranges and publish a same-day follow-up release so GitHub Dependabot resolves the undici manifest alerts against a pinned safe version.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: dependabot,dependencies,pm-cli,release,security
